    "description": "<p>S P Jain School of Global Management is a young, innovative business school with footprints in Dubai, Singapore, Sydney and Mumbai offering undergraduate and postgraduate programs in business management, the school’s MBA programs has been accredited by TEQSA.</p>\n<p>Our MBA 1 year program has been ranked top 20 best International MBA program from 2013 - 2019.&nbsp;Financial Times has also ranked our Global MBA programs in the Top 100 for 2011 and 2012.</p>\n<p>Being an innovative education provider, globalization is the heart of our teaching philosophy. Students spend time at all 3 campuses broadening their horizons, making them culturally sensitive and adaptable for any global role.</p>\n<p>S P Jain currently has 4 campuses – Sydney, Singapore, Dubai and Mumbai.&nbsp;</p>",
